From e3457f2840a29f8efa93ec1d72efb548914942c6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Parth Gajjar <parth.gajjar@amd.com>
Date: Mon, 12 Jan 2026 05:03:23 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Making kernel driver compatible with 6.18 kernel

Updating below APIs
hrtimer_init -> hr_timer_setup
del_timer_sync -> timer_delete_sync
del_timer -> timer_delete
del_timer_sync -> timer_delete_sync
__SetPageMovable -> SetPageMovableOps

Removed below APIs/callbacks
 .fence_value_str
__ClearPageMovable

Upstream-Status: Inappropriate [Xilinx Specific]
Signed-off-by: Parth Gajjar <parth.gajjar@amd.com>
---
 drivers/gpu/arm/midgard/Kbuild                | 19 +++++++--
 .../midgard/arbiter/mali_kbase_arbiter_pm.c   |  5 +++
 .../backend/gpu/mali_kbase_irq_linux.c        |  7 +++-
 .../midgard/backend/gpu/mali_kbase_jm_hw.c    |  5 +++
 .../backend/gpu/mali_kbase_js_backend.c       |  5 +++
 .../backend/gpu/mali_kbase_pm_driver.c        |  9 +++++
 .../backend/gpu/mali_kbase_pm_metrics.c       |  5 +++
 .../midgard/csf/mali_kbase_csf_scheduler.c    |  8 +++-
 .../gpu/arm/midgard/mali_kbase_fence_ops.c    | 12 +++++-
 drivers/gpu/arm/midgard/mali_kbase_jd.c       |  5 +++
 drivers/gpu/arm/midgard/mali_kbase_js.c       |  5 +++
 .../arm/midgard/mali_kbase_kinstr_prfcnt.c    |  5 +++
 .../gpu/arm/midgard/mali_kbase_mem_migrate.c  | 40 ++++++++++++++-----
